raw_text = "~ start
# approx 12 noon-ish time
do Story.set_location(\"lecture_hall\")
Naomi: Good morning everyone!
Naomi: img: naomi/18
Naomi: We have just a few announcements and some work for any willing volunteers!
Mabel: 👋👀
Caleb: Morning Naomi, and everyone
Player: Good morning!
Naomi: 😊
Naomi: Before I forget, here's your weekly grant
- [Claim] [#dollar] [if PhoneUnlocks.is_claimed(\"Photo1\") == false]
	set PhoneUnlocks.claim = \"Photo1\"
	set PhoneUnlocks.dollars += 1
- [Already Claimed] [if PhoneUnlocks.is_claimed(\"Photo1\") == true]
Mabel: OMG I'M RICH! 🤑
if Story.has_flag(\"LOVE\"):
	Mabel: img: mabel/107
else:
	Mabel: img: mabel/108
Player: Haha 😆
Caleb: Thanks! 😄
Naomi: First I'll need a volunteer for a photoshoot by another club
Naomi: They would like a girl on some of their advertisements and they requested me funnily enough 😅
Naomi: But my schedule is super packed this week so is @Paige around?
Player: Maybe she has class?
Naomi: That's true
Naomi: Anyway, Mabel could you help out?
Mabel: Wh- me!? 😳
Naomi: Yeah, you're a charming girl 😊
Naomi: I'm sure they'd be happy to accept you as the model
Mabel: But I've never done anything like that before.. 🙈
Naomi: I wouldn't have picked you if I didn't think you were right for the job!
- Don't worry too much babe!
	Player: Don't worry too much babe!
- You can do it!
	Player: You can do it!
Mabel: O-oh okay if you say so 😇 I'll do my best
Mabel: Which club is it?
if Story.has_flag(\"LOVE\"):
	Naomi: I'll be sending you to work with the tennis club
	Mabel: Tennis club?
	Naomi: Yes! They'd like a cover girl for their club posters since they're having trouble attracting girls to the club
	Naomi: They want to show it's for everyone
	Mabel: Oh I see, I guess that's nice
	Naomi: Perfect!
	Mabel: Will I be going alone? 😳
	Naomi: Actually the club is quite close to your boyfriend's campus!
	Naomi: I'm sure he can help and take the photos for the club!
	Mabel: Wow lucky me! 🥰
	Player: Lucky me too!
else:
	Naomi: I'll be sending you to work with the weekend club
	Naomi: They run the weekend night club parties, they're a pretty big deal!
	Mabel: Wow really?
	Naomi: Mhmm, their usual cover girl is really sick so they need someone to fill in
	Naomi: They are advertising one of their new club outfits for sale
	Mabel: Oh wow.. Uhm. Okay! 
	Mabel: I hope they don't need me to dance
	Naomi: Haha, it's just a photoshoot. I don't think they'll expect you to do anything more than that
	Mabel: Oh okay, I guess I could do that 😊
	Mabel: Will I be going alone? 😳
	Naomi: Actually the club is quite close to Caleb's building!
	Naomi: I'm sure he can help you and take the photos too!
	Mabel: I'd like someone to come with me 🥹
	Mabel: I wish it could be you babe, but thanks Caleb!
	Player: Me too!
	- But you should trust Caleb!
		Player: But you should trust Caleb!
		Caleb: img: caleb/4
		Naomi: Caleb! 😂
	- You should trust yourself a bit more!
		Player: You should trust yourself a bit more!
	Naomi: Don't worry, Caleb is a total professional when it comes to this thing
	Naomi: You'll feel perfectly at ease
	Caleb: Awh shucks, I try my best 😃
Naomi: We'll also do a mini training session tomorrow
Mabel: Tomorrow!? 🤯
Naomi: Yup! The shoot is the day after that
Mabel: SO SOON! 😭
Naomi: Don't worry, it'll be fine! I promise haha 😊
Naomi: These are just some of the club duties
- Babe, you got this!
	Player: Babe, you got this!
- Listen to Naomi Mabes 😘
	Player: Listen to Naomi Mabes
Mabel: Gee if you guys say so 🥹
Naomi: Alright that settles that, in other news
Naomi: Paige is missing but is Alice here?
Alice: I'm here...
Naomi: Good morning Alice!
Naomi: I need a volunteer to help them with their photography. Just show them the basics you learned from me or Caleb.
Naomi: Caleb is around to help one but could anyone else help?
Mabel: I'd help Alice out but I'm already with the photoshoot now 🥺
Alice: T-that's okay, you don't have to push yourself for me
Mabel: Next time! 😁
Naomi: I can probably squeeze one of them in my schedule but I'd rather somebody not rush them through it
- I can help Alice [#whiteheart]
	set Story.flag = \"Alice1\"
	Player: I can help Alice
	Alice: Oh uhm.. I.
	Alice: You don't have to
	Naomi: Great! Caleb can help Paige then
- I can help Paige [#blueheart]
	set Story.flag = \"Paige1\"
	Player: I can help Paige
	Naomi: Great! Caleb can help Alice then
- [Say Nothing]
	set Story.flag = \"Nobody1\"
	Naomi: I suppose it's a busy week for everyone then!
	Naomi: Alright I'll figure out how to squeeze you into my schedule. We can chat about this later Caleb
Caleb: Sounds good!
Naomi: I'll let you all organize your own meet ups
Naomi: But that's all for today, I gotta run to a meeting
Naomi: Have a nice week!
do social_post(\"jason_club_closed\")
do social_post(\"caleb_match\")
=> END"
metadata/dialogue_manager_version = "3.7.1"
